      data:
        modules:
        - weight: 25
          module:
            rid: 2308102993291247683
          output: "Our faithful have quelled the inferno and pulled the laborers
            from the ash! Better yet, the master of the manufactory and his workers
            have begged to be inducted into our Order. \n[+30 Flock]"
        - weight: 50
          module:
            rid: 2308102993291247692
          output: "Our faithful managed to put out the fires, yet alas, they could
            not reach the trapped workers in time. At the very least, the master
            of the manufactory has seen fit to reward our efforts. \n[+10 Wealth]"
        - weight: 25
          module:
            rid: 2308102993291247696
          output: "A grim tragedy! Our brave brethren perished in the flames while
            attempting to rescue the trapped. May the Beholder welcome our martyrs
            with open arms. \n[No Change]"
